## Vision  
Create a workplace culture at Green Destinations Travel Agency to attract, retain, and nurture talents by encouraging employee engagement, 
growth opportunities, and support systems.

## Scope  
- Analyze employee attrition trends and root causes.  
- Improve onboarding processes and mentorship programs.  
- Expand employee engagement initiatives.  
- Develop clear career development pathways.  
- Implement regular, transparent communication about retention efforts.

## Out of Scope  
- Salary restructuring or compensation redesign.  
- External recruitment processes.

## Objectives  
- Reduce overall attrition rate from 13.3% to below 10% within 12 months.  
- Increase employee satisfaction and engagement scores.  
- Strengthen retention especially during the first years of employment.
